{
  "materi": "fungsi-komposisi-invers",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "A",
      "title": "Pengertian Fungsi",
      "contoh": [
        {
          "section": "A",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 1",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan domain dari $f(x) = 5x^3 - 2x + 7$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> $f(x)$ adalah fungsi polinomial, tidak ada batasan nilai $x$. $$D_f = \\mathbb{R}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "A",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 2",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan domain dari $f(x) = \\dfrac{3x + 1}{x^2 - 5x + 6}$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Syarat: penyebut $\\neq 0$. $$x^2-5x+6 \\neq 0 \\implies (x-2)(x-3) \\neq 0$$ $$x \\neq 2 \\quad \\text{dan} \\quad x \\neq 3$$ $$D_f = \\mathbb{R} \\setminus \\{2,\\, 3\\}$$ <div class=\"grafik-wrap\" style=\"margin-top:.75rem;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 320 75\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:320px;\"><defs><marker id=\"nl2\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,1 L6,3.5 L0,6z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"308\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl2)\"/><line x1=\"308\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl2)\"/><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"308\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><circle cx=\"180\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"var(--surface-2,#fff)\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><circle cx=\"220\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"var(--surface-2,#fff)\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"100\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><line x1=\"140\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"140\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"140\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><line x1=\"180\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"180\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#EF4444\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><line x1=\"220\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"220\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#EF4444\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><line x1=\"260\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"260\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"72\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">semua x, kecuali x = 2 dan x = 3</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "A",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 3",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan domain dari $f(x) = \\sqrt{2x - 8}$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Syarat: ekspresi dalam akar $\\geq 0$. $$2x - 8 \\geq 0 \\implies 2x \\geq 8 \\implies x \\geq 4$$ $$D_f = \\{x \\in \\mathbb{R} \\mid x \\geq 4\\}$$ <div class=\"grafik-wrap\" style=\"margin-top:.75rem;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 320 75\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:320px;\"><defs><marker id=\"nl3\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,1 L6,3.5 L0,6z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"308\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl3)\"/><line x1=\"308\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl3)\"/><!-- Interval hijau: x≥4, origin=60, scale=40: x=0→60, x=1→100, x=2→140, x=3→180, x=4→220 --><line x1=\"220\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"305\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><!-- Titik tertutup x=4 --><circle cx=\"220\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#059669\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><!-- Ticks --><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"60\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"100\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><line x1=\"140\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"140\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"140\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><line x1=\"180\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"180\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><line x1=\"220\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"220\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><line x1=\"260\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"260\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"72\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">x ≥ 4</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "A",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 4",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan domain dari $f(x) = \\sqrt{-x^2 + 4x + 5}$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Syarat: $-x^2+4x+5 \\geq 0$. Kalikan $-1$ (balik tanda ketidaksamaan): $$x^2-4x-5 \\leq 0 \\implies (x-5)(x+1) \\leq 0$$ $$-1 \\leq x \\leq 5$$ $$D_f = \\{x \\in \\mathbb{R} \\mid -1 \\leq x \\leq 5\\}$$ <div class=\"grafik-wrap\" style=\"margin-top:.75rem;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 320 75\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:320px;\"><defs><marker id=\"nl4\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,1 L6,3.5 L0,6z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"308\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl4)\"/><line x1=\"308\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl4)\"/><!-- origin=80, scale=40: x=-1→40, x=0→80, x=2→160, x=4→240, x=5→280 --><line x1=\"40\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><!-- Titik tertutup di -1 dan 5 --><circle cx=\"40\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#059669\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"280\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#059669\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><!-- Ticks --><line x1=\"40\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"40\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"40\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-1</text><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"80\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><line x1=\"160\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"160\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text><line x1=\"240\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"240\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text><line x1=\"280\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"280\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"72\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-1 ≤ x ≤ 5</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "A",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 5",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan domain dari $f(x) = \\dfrac{x+3}{\\sqrt{x^2 - x - 6}}$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Penyebut mengandung akar, syarat: $x^2 - x - 6 > 0$. $$(x-3)(x+2) > 0$$ Titik kritis $x = -2$ dan $x = 3$. Uji tanda: positif di $x < -2$ dan $x > 3$. $$D_f = \\{x \\in \\mathbb{R} \\mid x < -2 \\text{ atau } x > 3\\}$$ <div class=\"grafik-wrap\" style=\"margin-top:.75rem;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 320 90\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:320px;\"><defs><marker id=\"nl5\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,1 L6,3.5 L0,6z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"46\" x2=\"308\" y2=\"46\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl5)\"/><line x1=\"308\" y1=\"46\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"46\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl5)\"/><!-- origin=160, scale=40: x=-2→80, x=0→160, x=3→280 --><!-- Interval kiri: x<-2 --><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"46\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"46\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><!-- Interval kanan: x>3 --><line x1=\"280\" y1=\"46\" x2=\"305\" y2=\"46\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><!-- Interval tengah: -2<x<3 (tidak termasuk domain) --><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"46\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"46\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.4\"/><!-- Titik terbuka x=-2 dan x=3 --><circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"46\" r=\"6\" fill=\"var(--surface-2,#fff)\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><circle cx=\"280\" cy=\"46\" r=\"6\" fill=\"var(--surface-2,#fff)\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><!-- Tanda uji tanda --><text x=\"42\" y=\"34\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(+)</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"34\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#EF4444\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(−)</text><text x=\"293\" y=\"34\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">(+)</text><!-- Ticks --><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"52\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"80\" y=\"66\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#EF4444\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-2</text><line x1=\"160\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"52\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"160\" y=\"66\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><line x1=\"280\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"52\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"280\" y=\"66\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#EF4444\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"82\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">x &lt; -2 atau x &gt; 3</text></svg></div>"
        },
        {
          "section": "A",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 6",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Tentukan domain dari $f(x) = \\sqrt{x+4} + \\dfrac{1}{x-1}$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Dua syarat sekaligus: <ul style=\"margin-top:.4rem;\"><li>Syarat akar: $x+4 \\geq 0 \\Rightarrow x \\geq -4$</li><li>Syarat penyebut: $x-1 \\neq 0 \\Rightarrow x \\neq 1$</li></ul> Irisan kedua syarat: $$D_f = \\{x \\in \\mathbb{R} \\mid x \\geq -4, \\, x \\neq 1\\}$$ <div class=\"grafik-wrap\" style=\"margin-top:.75rem;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 320 75\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:320px;\"><defs><marker id=\"nl6\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,1 L6,3.5 L0,6z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"308\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl6)\"/><line x1=\"308\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" marker-end=\"url(#nl6)\"/><!-- origin=240, scale=40: x=-4→80, x=-2→160, x=0→240, x=1→280 --><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"38\" x2=\"305\" y2=\"38\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><!-- Titik tertutup x=-4 --><circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#059669\" stroke=\"#059669\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><!-- Titik kosong x=1 --><circle cx=\"280\" cy=\"38\" r=\"6\" fill=\"var(--surface-2,#fff)\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"/><!-- Ticks --><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"80\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-4</text><line x1=\"160\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"160\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">-2</text><line x1=\"240\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"240\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#94A3B8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">0</text><line x1=\"280\" y1=\"32\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/><text x=\"280\" y=\"58\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#EF4444\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text><text x=\"160\" y=\"72\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#059669\" text-anchor=\"middle\">x ≥ -4, kecuali x = 1</text></svg></div>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "B",
      "title": "Komposisi Fungsi",
      "contoh": [
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 7",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Misalkan $f = \\{(1,4),(2,3),(3,1),(4,2)\\}$ dan $g = \\{(1,2),(2,4),(3,1),(4,3)\\}$. Tentukan $f \\circ g$ dan $g \\circ f$.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>$f \\circ g$:</strong> setiap $x$ dipetakan $g$ dulu, lalu hasilnya dipetakan $f$.<br> $(1,2)\\to f(2)=3$, $(2,4)\\to f(4)=2$, $(3,1)\\to f(1)=4$, $(4,3)\\to f(3)=1$<br> $\\Rightarrow f \\circ g = \\{(1,3),(2,2),(3,4),(4,1)\\}$<br><br><strong>$g \\circ f$:</strong> setiap $x$ dipetakan $f$ dulu, lalu hasilnya dipetakan $g$.<br> $(1,4)\\to g(4)=3$, $(2,3)\\to g(3)=1$, $(3,1)\\to g(1)=2$, $(4,2)\\to g(2)=4$<br> $\\Rightarrow g \\circ f = \\{(1,3),(2,1),(3,2),(4,4)\\}$<br><br> Terlihat $f \\circ g \\neq g \\circ f$ — membuktikan sifat tidak komutatif."
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 8",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $f(x) = 2x - 1$ dan $g(x) = x^2 - 3x + 5$.<br>Tentukan $(f \\circ g)(x)$ dan $(g \\circ f)(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "$$(f \\circ g)(x) = f[x^2-3x+5]$$ $$= 2(x^2-3x+5)-1 = \\mathbf{2x^2-6x+9}$$ $$(g \\circ f)(x) = g[2x-1]$$ $$= (2x-1)^2-3(2x-1)+5$$ $$= 4x^2-10x+9 = \\mathbf{4x^2-10x+9}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 9",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $f(x) = \\dfrac{2x-3}{7-3x}$ dan $g(x) = 4x + 2$. Tentukan $(f \\circ g)(x)$ dan $(g \\circ f)(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "$$(f \\circ g)(x) = f[4x+2] = \\frac{2(4x+2)-3}{7-3(4x+2)}$$ $$= \\frac{8x+1}{1-12x}$$ $$(g \\circ f)(x) = g\\!\\left[\\frac{2x-3}{7-3x}\\right]$$ $$= 4\\!\\left(\\frac{2x-3}{7-3x}\\right)+2$$ $$= \\frac{8x-12+2(7-3x)}{7-3x} = \\frac{2x+2}{7-3x}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 10",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $f(x) = 2x + 3$. Tentukan $(f \\circ f \\circ f)(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "$$(f \\circ f)(x) = f[2x+3] = 2(2x+3)+3 = 4x+9$$ $$(f \\circ f \\circ f)(x) = f[4x+9]$$ $$= 2(4x+9)+3 = \\mathbf{8x+21}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 11",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $f(x) = x^2 - 5x + 4$ dan $g(x) = x^2 + 3x - 6$.<br>Tentukan nilai $(f \\circ g)(2)$ dan $(g \\circ f)(3)$.</p>",
          "p": "$$g(2) = 4+6-6 = 4$$ $$(f \\circ g)(2) = f(4) = 16-20+4 = \\mathbf{0}$$ $$f(3) = 9-15+4 = -2$$ $$(g \\circ f)(3) = g(-2) = 4-6-6 = \\mathbf{-8}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 12",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $(f \\circ h)(x) = 2x^2 - 4x - 3$ dan $h(x) = x + 3$. Tentukan $f(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Karena $f[x+3] = 2x^2-4x-3$, misalkan $m = x+3$, maka $x = m-3$: $$f(m) = 2(m-3)^2-4(m-3)-3$$ $$= 2m^2-12m+18-4m+12-3$$ $$= 2m^2-16m+27$$ Jadi $f(x) = 2x^2-16x+27$."
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 13",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $(f \\circ h)(x) = 4x^2 + 6x - 5$ dan $f(x) = 2x - 1$. Tentukan $h(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "$$f[h(x)] = 4x^2+6x-5$$ $$\\implies 2\\cdot h(x)-1 = 4x^2+6x-5$$ $$\\implies h(x) = \\mathbf{2x^2+3x-2}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 14",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $(f \\circ g)(x) = 2x^2 - 6x + 7$ dan $g(x) = x^2 - 3x + 4$. Tentukan $f(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Misalkan $m = g(x) = x^2-3x+4$, maka $2m = 2x^2-6x+8$.<br> Perhatikan $2m-1 = 2x^2-6x+7 = (f \\circ g)(x)$, sehingga: $$f(m) = 2m-1 \\implies \\mathbf{f(x) = 2x-1}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 15",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $(g \\circ f)(x) = \\dfrac{x-4}{x+3}$ dan $g(x) = 3x - 2$. Tentukan $f(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "$$3\\cdot f(x)-2 = \\frac{x-4}{x+3}$$ $$\\implies 3\\cdot f(x) = \\frac{x-4}{x+3}+\\frac{2(x+3)}{x+3} = \\frac{3x+2}{x+3}$$ $$\\implies f(x) = \\mathbf{\\frac{3x+2}{3(x+3)}}$$"
        },
        {
          "section": "B",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 16",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $f(2x+1) = 4x^2 - 8x + 5$. Tentukan $f(x)$.</p>",
          "p": "<br> Misalkan $m = 2x+1$, sehingga $x = \\dfrac{m-1}{2}$. Substitusi: $$f(m) = 4\\!\\left(\\frac{m-1}{2}\\right)^2 - 8\\!\\left(\\frac{m-1}{2}\\right) + 5$$ $$= (m-1)^2-4(m-1)+5 = m^2-6m+10$$ Jadi $f(x) = x^2-6x+10$."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "C",
      "title": "Fungsi Invers",
      "contoh": [
        {
          "section": "C",
          "label": "📘 Contoh 17",
          "q": "<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:.9rem;\">Diketahui $f(x) = \\sqrt{2x - 4}$. Tentukan $f^{-1}(x)$, serta nyatakan domain dan range-nya.</p>",
          "p": "<br><strong>Langkah 1 — Tentukan $D_f$ dan $R_f$:</strong> $$2x - 4 \\geq 0 \\implies x \\geq 2 \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad D_f = [2,\\,+\\infty), \\quad R_f = [0,\\,+\\infty)$$ <strong>Langkah 2 — Cari rumus $f^{-1}$:</strong> Misalkan $y = \\sqrt{2x-4}$: $$y^2 = 2x - 4 \\implies x = \\frac{y^2 + 4}{2}$$ Jadi $f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{x^2+4}{2}$.<br><br><strong>Langkah 3 — Terapkan prinsip $D_{f^{-1}} = R_f$ dan $R_{f^{-1}} = D_f$:</strong> $$D_{f^{-1}} = R_f = [0,\\,+\\infty), \\qquad R_{f^{-1}} = D_f = [2,\\,+\\infty)$$ <strong>Verifikasi:</strong> $(f^{-1} \\circ f)(x) = f^{-1}\\!\\bigl[\\sqrt{2x-4}\\bigr] = \\dfrac{(\\sqrt{2x-4})^2+4}{2} = \\dfrac{2x-4+4}{2} = x$ ✓"
