          "p": "<br><strong>a.</strong> Misalkan $y = x^2 - 6x + 5$, lengkapi kuadrat sempurna: $$y - 5 + 9 = x^2 - 6x + 9 \\implies y + 4 = (x-3)^2 \\implies x = 3 \\pm \\sqrt{y+4}$$ Jadi $f^{-1}(x) = 3 \\pm \\sqrt{x+4}$.<br><br><strong>b.</strong> Misalkan $y = 2x^2 - 8x + 4$: $$\\frac{y}{2} = x^2 - 4x + 2 \\implies \\frac{y}{2} + 2 = x^2 - 4x + 4 = (x-2)^2$$ $$x - 2 = \\pm\\sqrt{\\frac{y}{2}+2} = \\pm\\frac{\\sqrt{2y+8}}{2} \\implies x = \\frac{4 \\pm \\sqrt{2y+8}}{2}$$ Jadi $f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{4 \\pm \\sqrt{2x+8}}{2}$."
